│   // ...                                                                                                                                                                                 │
│ }                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ This doesn't check for `nsw`. If the negation has `nsw`, this transform is unsafe. I will add a check to prevent this. A simple way is to check if the `sub` that implements the         │
│ negation has the `nsw` flag.                                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                                                                                   │
